{{about|the novel|the film|Lost in Translation (film)|the 1989 memoir by Eva Hoffman|Lost in Translation (memoir)|the 1974 poem by [[James Merrill]]|Lost in Translation (poem)}}
{{Multiple issues|
{{refimprove|date=February 2015}}
{{notability|Books|date=February 2015}}
